    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a master of physics by launching your car into the air, performing kickflips, and grinding rails.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290330/extras/804e8c4e6bfa87b48b6c19cae550e14f.poster.avif?t=1764873812\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290330/extras/804e8c4e6bfa87b48b6c19cae550e14f.webm?t=1764873812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290330/extras/804e8c4e6bfa87b48b6c19cae550e14f.mp4?t=1764873812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You control the rotation of the car directly. There are no animations that play when you enter a button combo, so it's up to you to perform the trick.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The replay editor that lets you rewind time to capture and share exciting moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accomplish missions to unlock levels and cosmetics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play alone, or online with friends. Every feature will work in either mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
